# Contact form -> email, via Web3Forms (free plan = client-side submit).
#
# 1. Sign up at https://web3forms.com using your destination inbox
#    (currently vansalesapp@gmail.com).
# 2. Create an access key for that inbox.
# 3. Copy this file to .env.local and paste the key below.
#
# NOTE: the free plan submits from the browser, so this key is PUBLIC
# (NEXT_PUBLIC_*) and ships in the client bundle. It can only post to the
# inbox tied to the key. To keep the key secret, move to a server-side sender
# (Resend / SMTP) later — see docs/WEB-TODO.md.
#
NEXT_PUBLIC_WEB3FORMS_ACCESS_KEY=
